{"tid":86460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 曾俊華選舉 Facebook 專頁已開","createTime":"2017-01-19T05:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T11:10:23.000Z","uid":6604,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c71995574a05a4aafc7b70608e5962d5c6fdaccf","tid":86460,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"Source: 眾新聞 facebook<br />\n<br />\n財爺曾俊華今日向傳媒發採訪通知，宣佈下午3時半開記者會之後，他在幾分鐘前再開通了一個新的Facebook專頁，短時間已吸引數百LIKE。<br />\n<br />\n財爺一向有玩Facebook習慣，文章更引來大量網民追蹤，不過以前都是用私人賬戶，今日就新開了一個專頁。專頁以「團結、希望、信任」等字眼為Cover Photo，版面描述更是：「只要有你們繼續與我同行，又何懼前路新挑戰？」專頁貼文指自己即將舉行記者會，屆時將會在專頁進行直播，財爺似乎已為參選特首做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/johntsangpage/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjohntsangpage%2F&d=s6l9MFVJgpHrcry9F5uOIEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=f4238360\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/johntsangpage/</a>"},{"pid":"015cf3faf84f653221a5de6155e9311cf462c36f","tid":86460,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T05:59:34.000Z","msg":"已經有5000幾人like左。"},{"pid":"b4e12666391c98e38d2de2aa0d2566d8875faecc","tid":86460,"uid":40308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb4f8f3982a57230fe1b4320a2bb74861b82a3d","tid":86460,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:10:54.000Z","msg":"梁粉放晒風話佢今日宣佈棄選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又假傳中央聖旨"},{"pid":"ff51f3c086fd81e1545ce9909d63632c330c96b6","tid":86460,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:29:48.000Z","msg":"Facebook 做live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eaf12d8a710fd6e91e585397d54efa229571813","tid":86460,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"